rows.label: tev025301_MSG0001
rows.name: This is Mission Control. As a BLADE, you can... Hmm?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0002
rows.name:
Oh! I see that you haven't yet registered as a BLADE,
[ST:playername ].[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0003
rows.name:
Well, if you do register and join a division,
you'll be able to accept missions right here.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0004
rows.name:
I understand that you haven't yet decided what role
you wish to play here in New LA, and that's fine.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0005
rows.name: But I believe you would make a splendid BLADE.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0006
rows.name:
Trust me, I've seen off countless BLADEs standing right
here. I know talent when I see it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0008
rows.name:
My name is Eleonora, and I serve as BLADE's
receptionist.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0010
rows.name:
If you have any questions about your
assignments, feel free to ask me anything.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0011
rows.name:
If there is anything that I can do to help,
I hope you'll let me be of service.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0012
rows.name:
Now go do your best, [ST:playername ]!
I expect great things from you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0020
rows.name:
BLADEs must join a division before they're able to
use Mission Control.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0021
rows.name:
Once you have completed your data probe installation
mission, you should be ready to select a division.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0022
rows.name:
At that point, please come speak to me again.
I'm sure I will have something that strikes your fancy.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0027
rows.name:
Are you worried about me? Oh, thank you.
I'm touched by the concern, but I'm fine. Really.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0028
rows.name:
Maybe it would be better if you posed that same
question to the people of New LA.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0029
rows.name:
I am sure there are many who are troubled by
something, but don't consider it significant enough to
make a formal request of BLADE.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0039
rows.name:
Your training just ended, but you're already being sent
out to track down Nelson's missing team?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0040
rows.name:
Commander Vandham must have taken quite a shine
to you![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0041
rows.name:
That man asks a great deal of his BLADEs, but he
only makes such requests to the ones he believes are
up to the task.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0042
rows.name:
Nelson's team was in the southeast part of Primordia
when we lost contact with them. I wish you the best of
luck with your search.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0043
rows.name:
Oh, but I should mention one thing—if you're willing
to pursue multiple missions at the same time,
take a look at Mission Control before heading out.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0058
rows.name:
Welcome back, [ST:playername ].
I hope your search was successful.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0059
rows.name:
If you're ready to report, please speak directly with
Commander Vandham in the BLADE barracks.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0060
rows.name:
I know he was eager to assess your performance on
this task personally.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0077
rows.name:
Welcome back, [ST:playername ].
Have you become accustomed to BLADE work?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0078
rows.name:
If you've gained confidence in your abilities, perhaps
this would be a good time to challenge yourself by
paying a visit to Noctilum far northwest of New LA?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0079
rows.name:
We've yet to make any significant progress installing
data probes in that region.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0080
rows.name:
And expanding FrontierNav may allow us to witness
some significant development.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0081
rows.name:
But of course, if you don't believe you're ready for
that yet, you can continue to acclimate yourself to
BLADE work by pursuing jobs from Mission Control.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0098
rows.name:
Our newest immigrant, L, can be found down
Armory Alley.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0099
rows.name:
It's quite heartening to have a Miran native fighting by
our side![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0100
rows.name:
Of course, he IS just one man, but I assume he has
friends or the like.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0101
rows.name:
...What's that? He's the only one of his kind?
Well then, I hope he'll be able to make plenty of
friends for himself here in New LA![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0106
rows.name: Have you visited the Ma-non ship yet?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0107
rows.name:
There's a warp device directly in front of BLADE HQ
that can take you straight to it.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0108
rows.name:
I couldn't begin to tell you how the warp device works,
though our mechanics are investigating the matter.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0109
rows.name:
But apparently all they've been able to ascertain is
that it has no harmful effects on our mimeosomes.
...Or so they claim.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0110
rows.name:
Still, I can't help but wonder what would happen if
another lifeform was there at the instant you warped.
Wouldn't you end up being fused together?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0115
rows.name:
The machine that was recovered is currently being
examined at the restricted hangar in the lower level.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0116
rows.name:
It isn't yet clear why it had been abandoned where it
was found.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0117
rows.name:
But hopefully a careful examination will provide some
clues to our enemy's objective.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0118
rows.name: I do hope their analysis is completed soon.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0125
rows.name:
I heard what happened to the Lifehold Archive in
Oblivia. What a tragedy![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0126
rows.name:
I wonder what priceless data was stored in that unit...?
Ah, forgive me. I hope you don't take that as criticism
of your performance.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0127
rows.name:
The loss of the archive brings up the question of how
much this "Ganglion" organization knows about us
humans.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0128
rows.name:
I don't like being at war with an enemy who we know
nothing about, yet who knows a great deal about us.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0135
rows.name:
The BLADEs we lost have been taken to the Mimeosome
Maintenance Center.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0136
rows.name:
Commander Vandham has directed the center to revive
them if possible, but the chances seem slim.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0137
rows.name:
If only we'd been able to make a successful landing...
And if only we hadn't lost the White Whale.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0138
rows.name:
But there is no point in regretting the past.
We must focus on what we might yet achieve.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0139
rows.name:
Finding the Lifehold Core is our only hope now.
Please do not fail us, [ST:playername ]![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0145
rows.name:
I feel as though I've seen the leader of the Wrothians
before somewhere...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0146
rows.name:
Oh! Wasn't he the one who stole that Skell from the
restricted hangar?![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0147
rows.name:
I remember watching the security camera footage
with Commander Vandham and arguing over whether
the thief looked more like a cat or a dog.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0148
rows.name:
Ah, forgive me. That's...hardly relevant to anything.
I wish you the best of luck on your missions![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0153
rows.name:
The Lifehold Core is coming perilously close to running
out of operating time.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0154
rows.name:
I feel useless just sitting here, but I'm no warrior,
and I'd be a liability were I to join in the fight.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0155
rows.name:
I can only put my faith in BLADE.
In you, [ST:playername ].[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0156
rows.name:
Please, you have to find the Lifehold Core before the
countdown hits zero![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0161
rows.name: We're analyzing the location of the Lifehold Core.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0162
rows.name:
It will take some time, so perhaps you'd like to pursue
another assignment from Mission Control?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0163
rows.name:
Ah, that's right! I've heard from Commander Vandham
that the Skell flight tests have begun.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0164
rows.name:
He had quite the grin on his face as he was making
his way to the Outfitters test hangar earlier.
Perhaps you should head down there yourself.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0170
rows.name:
I understand that the analysis of the Lifehold Core
location is nearly complete.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0171
rows.name:
The Director General was making preparations for a
public address a short while ago.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0172
rows.name:
I assume that a new mission will be available shortly.
For now, you should hurry back to the barracks![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0177
rows.name:
A Skell with a flight module appears to be the only
means of reaching the coordinates where the Lifehold
Core landed.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0178
rows.name:
Perhaps you've noticed other areas that could only be
reached by air?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0179
rows.name:
Still, I'd ask you to make this mission your priority.
There will be plenty of time to explore Mira once the
Core is secure![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0180
rows.name: Not that I'm in any position to stop you, of course...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0185
rows.name: Welcome back, [ST:playername ]![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0186
rows.name:
I know that mission was a long and grueling one,
but it's all over now. You've done excellent work.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0187
rows.name:
Still, I hope you don't intend to declare the job finished
and return to the barracks to roll around with your pets
all day![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0188
rows.name:
There are still a great many missions that await you
both here in New LA, and in Mira beyond.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev025301_MSG0189
rows.name:
We may not be in our mimeosomes for long,
so this is the time to challenge all of the difficult 
missions you wouldn't dare attempt otherwise.[ST:wait ]
